             was indicted <rs id="t17741019-28-off124" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17741019-28-off124" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17741019-28-off124" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               for forging a certain order for the payment of money
            </rs>; which said forged order is as followeth: ( that is to say)</p>
               <p>Messrs. Drummond.</p>
               <p>Pay the bearer the sum of fifteen pounds, and place it to the account of</p>
               <p>J. Pownall.</p>
               <p>September 8, 1774.</p>
               <p>with intention to defraud 
               
